comments: Barnes (TOR) brings his hands toward Tucker (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as Barnes (TOR) releases away to roll.
Barnes (TOR) jumps vertically and absorbs the ensuing contact that occurs defending Harden's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) firms up in Tucker's (PHI) path and absorbs the incidental contact that occurs as the pick is set.
Embiid (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Siakam (TOR) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Barnes (TOR) briefly places his hands on Harden (PHI) and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Barnes (TOR) dislodges the ball out of bounds. The 76ers retain possession of the ball.
Tucker (PHI) steps into Siakam's (TOR) path and initiates body contact, which affects his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending by Embiid (PHI) is overturned and no basket is scored.
VanVleet (TOR) is moving alongside Melton's (PHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during Melton's (PHI) drive.
Harden (PHI) and Barnes (TOR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in Barnes's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Tucker (PHI) moves alongside Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Siakam (TOR) on the perimeter.
Embiid (PHI) moves alongside Anunoby's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs as he contest the driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball away as he contests Harden's (PHI) driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Barnes (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Tucker (PHI) delivers contact to Barnes (TOR) that causes him to lose his balance, forcing him to make contact with Harris (PHI) as he returns to the floor.
Siakam (TOR) gathers the ball and takes three steps before releasing the pass.
Barnes (TOR) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Barnes' (TOR) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and a 24 second violation is correctly called.
Melton (PHI) is not established in Barnes' (TOR) path and delivers illegal contact that affects Barnes' (TOR) defensive position.
Tucker (PHI) briefly reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Siakam (TOR). There is no contact made during Siakam's shooting motion.
Melton (PHI) establishes himself in Barnes's (TOR) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Boucher (TOR) initiates contact with Melton's (PHI) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the OOB called on Melton (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful, as he is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB.
Embiid (PHI) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Embiid (PHI) and Boucher (TOR) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
